response.overview: From 3 mobile trailers to over 60 locations today, Valley Health has spent half a century delivering high quality, compassionate care to their neighbors, regardless of their ability to pay. This powerful documentary traces the health centerâ€™s origins and journey of growth, spotlighting the people, stories and heart behind one of the largest integrated Community Health Centers in the nation. Rooted in service and driven by a heart for neighbors, the documentary chronicles & celebrates their 50 year journey and legacy, and their ongoing work to deliver neighbor-centered care for another 50 forward.
